  "description": {
    "main": "This Philips Ambilight 32” TV splashes your walls with colour for super immersive entertainment. LED lights on the back of the TV dance along to whatever's showing, stretching the action beyond the frame. The Pixel Plus Full HD engine works tirelessly to boost the sharpness, motion, and vibrancy of every scene. Plus, HDR10 and HLG support mean you'll get to see all the detail, from the darkest scenes to the brightest lights. The high dynamic range (HDR) boosts colour and contrast so everything will look as good as you expect.",
